data.description:
Beautiful home on a family-friendly street with cul-de-sac.  Open concept design downstairs with natural lighting and vaulted ceilings.  Granite countertops, recently updated stainless appliances, copper sink, and bar stool seating in the kitchen.  Dining area accommodates large table with room to spare.  Laundry room and pantry with kitchen and garage access.  Spacious living areas, and hardwood flooring throughout the house.  Master bedroom will allow oversize furniture and has walk-in closet, his and hers sinks, garden tub, and separate shower. Plenty of space for the whole family to spread out with 3 additional bedrooms and 2.5 additional bathrooms (includes mother-in-law suite). Bonus room on the main level and bonus room upstairs both offer endless possibilities for office space or playroom. Covered backyard patio and spacious yard makes for great entertaining.  Conveniently located to nearby shopping, restaurants, interstate access, and 25 minutes from downtown Birmingham. This home is the perfect combination of space, location, and price!

Contact owner at 205-957-3973 to schedule a showing.
data.whatILove: Quiet neighborhood with sidewalks throughout, easy access, cul-de-sac, roominess, and feels like home.
